(249846, 520, 2, 'The history of our brand started from pure enthusiasm. At the beginning, about 5 years ago we were a small team of dreamers. It was important to us how we looked and how looked those around us. We wanted to make our own contribution in this regard. We started with the consulting services of clothing, footwear and accessories manufacturers. The consulting services included global services, related to marketing and sales, but also scrupulous details down to the particularities of production. For us it was important that the garnment or the accessory should not only look good on person, but also to be comfortable to wear. We went into the smallest details, such as: how the garnment should be hung in the bathroom, before the shower, how should the stitches highlight the strengths of the silhouette and vice versa, what kind of fabrics and patterns to use for to combat existing women\'s phobias.\n Over time, our team has grown. We have specialists with studies in clothing design, graphic design, Fashion marketing specialists. The experience gained led to two major conclusions: 1. all women want to look good, but not all have enough resources for it (time and money) 2. there are many manufacturers in the Fashion industry who put their heart into their work,but few have heard of them.\n As a result, we developed this platform, in which ladies have the chance to easily find clothing items from authentic brands, combined in adorable outfits by our team of fashionistas.\n Soledy is the acronym formed by the words \"So Lady\" and Sole Lady, which best expresses our motto: To look beautiful is an art, but also a necessity.\n Soledy - for ladies with a remarkable taste!\nAs result, we decided to create our own products. That is how the brand umbrella brand Soledy was created!', '2020-05-11 13:08:42', '2022-03-14 14:17:52'),
(249882, 520, 38, 'Istoria brand-ului nostru a inceput de la entusiasm curat. La început, circa 5 ani în urmă am fost o echipă mică de visătoare. Pentru noi era important cum arătam și cum arată cei din jur. Ne doream să aducem contribuție proprie în acest aspect. Am început cu serviciile de consultanță a producătorilor de haine, încalțăminte și accesorii. Serviciile de consultanță cuprindeau aspecte globale, ce țin de marketing și vânzări, dar și detalii scrupuloase pâna la particularități de producere. Pentru noi era important ca haina sau accesoriu nu doar să arate bine pe persoana, dar și să fie comodă la purtat. Intram in cele mai mici detalii, cum ar fi: de ce să fie agățată haina în baie, inainte de duș, cum să fie cusătura pentru a scoate în evidență punctele forte ale siluetei și invers, ce fel de stofe și modele să fie utilizate pentru a combate fobiile existente ale femeilor. \n Cu timpul echipa noastră a crescut. Avem specialiști cu studii în design vestimentar, design grafic, specialiști marketing din domeniul Fashion. Experiența acumulată a dus la două concluzii majore: 1. toate femeile vor să arate bine, dar nu toate au suficiente resurse pentru asta (timp și bani) 2. există mulți producători în industria Fashion, care-și pun inima în lucru său, dar nu cunosc cum să se facă auziți.\n Ca rezultat, am conceput această platformă, în care damele au șansă să găsească ușor articole vestimentare de la brand-uri veritabile, asortate în ținute adorabile de către echipa noastră de fashioniste.\n Soledy este acronimul format din cuvintele So Lady (atât de damă) și Sole + Lady (unical + damă), care exprimă cel mai bine motto-ul nostru: Să arăți frumos este o artă, dar și necesitate.\n Soledy - pentru dame cu gust remarcabil!\nCu timpul, am hotarit sa facem producere de haine și accesorii proprii. Iată cum a aparut brandul umbrela Soledy!', '2020-05-11 13:08:42', '2022-03-14 14:17:52'),
(249885, 520, 41, 'The history of our brand started from pure enthusiasm. At the beginning, about 5 years ago we were a small team of dreamers. It was important to us how we looked and how looked those around us. We wanted to make our own contribution in this regard. We started with the consulting services of clothing, footwear and accessories manufacturers. The consulting services included global services, related to marketing and sales, but also scrupulous details down to the particularities of production. For us it was important that the garnment or the accessory should not only look good on person, but also to be comfortable to wear. We went into the smallest details, such as: how the garnment should be hung in the bathroom, before the shower, how should the stitches highlight the strengths of the silhouette and vice versa, what kind of fabrics and patterns to use for to combat existing women\'s phobias.\n Over time, our team has grown. We have specialists with studies in clothing design, graphic design, Fashion marketing specialists. The experience gained led to two major conclusions: 1. all women want to look good, but not all have enough resources for it (time and money) 2. there are many manufacturers in the Fashion industry who put their heart into their work,but few have heard of them.\n As a result, we developed this platform, in which ladies have the chance to easily find clothing items from authentic brands, combined in adorable outfits by our team of fashionistas.\n Soledy is the acronym formed by the words \"So Lady\" and Sole Lady, which best expresses our motto: To look beautiful is an art, but also a necessity.\n Soledy - for ladies with a remarkable taste!\nAs result, we decided to create our own products. That is how the brand umbrella brand Soledy was created!', '2020-05-11 13:08:42', '2022-03-14 14:17:52'),
