(265890, 675, 47, 'RETURN AND REFUND PROCEDURE', '2020-09-04 06:40:42', '2022-03-14 14:17:53'),
(265891, 676, 2, 'The return procedure for products is subject to the legislation in force. If for any reason, you are not satisfied with your online purchase, you may return unused articles within 14 days of receipt (own expense). In order to return the order and obtain refund for payed goods from the order, you have to send the return to the WAREHOUSE’s address (disclosed on the first page of this policy).', '2020-09-04 06:40:42', '2022-03-14 14:17:53'),
(265892, 676, 38, 'Procedura de returnare a produselor este supusă legislației în vigoare. Dacă din orice motiv, nu sunteți mulțumit de achiziția online, puteți returna articolele neutilizate în termen de 14 zile de la data primirii comenzii (pe seama și cheltuială proprie). Pentru a returna comanda și a obține rambursarea mărfurilor plătite din comandă, trebuie să trimiteți returul pe adresa depozitului (afișată pe prima pagină a acestui document)', '2020-09-04 06:40:42', '2022-03-14 14:17:53'),
(265893, 676, 41, 'Процедура возврата товаров регулируется действующим законодательством. Если по какой-либо причине вы не удовлетворены своей покупкой через Интернет, вы можете вернуть неиспользованные товары в течение 14 дней с момента получения заказа (за свой счет). Чтобы вернуть заказ и получить возмещение за оплаченный товар из заказа, вы должны отправить возврат по адресу СКЛАД (указан на первой странице этого документа).', '2020-09-04 06:40:42', '2022-03-14 14:17:53'),
(265894, 676, 43, 'La procédure de retour des produits est soumise à la législation en vigueur. Si pour une raison quelconque, vous n\'êtes pas satisfait de votre achat en ligne, vous pouvez retourner les articles inutilisés dans les 14 jours suivant la réception (à vos frais). Afin de retourner la commande et d\'obtenir le remboursement des marchandises payées de la commande, vous devez envoyer le retour à l\'adresse de L\'ENTREPÔT (indiqué sur la première page de cette politique).', '2020-09-04 06:40:42', '2022-03-14 14:17:53'),
(265895, 676, 47, 'The return procedure for products is subject to the legislation in force. If for any reason, you are not satisfied with your online purchase, you may return unused articles within 14 days of receipt (own expense). In order to return the order and obtain refund for payed goods from the order, you have to send the return to the WAREHOUSE’s address (disclosed on the first page of this policy).', '2020-09-04 06:40:42', '2022-03-14 14:17:53'),
(265896, 677, 2, 'To return a product, it must be in the same state as it was delivered to you: the labels have to be attached to the products, have no signs of wearing. Any return that does not meet these conditions will be declined.', '2020-09-04 06:40:42', '2022-03-14 14:17:53'),
(265897, 677, 38, 'Pentru a returna un produs, acesta trebuie să fie în aceeași stare în care a fost livrat: etichetele trebuie să fie atașate de produse, să nu existe semne de purtare. Orice retur care nu îndeplinește aceste condiții va fi refuzat.', '2020-09-04 06:40:42', '2022-03-14 14:17:53'),
(265898, 677, 41, 'Чтобы вернуть товар, он должен быть в том же состоянии, в котором он был доставлен вам: этикетки должны быть прикреплены к товару, не иметь признаков износа. Любой возврат, который не соответствует этим условиям, будет отклонен.', '2020-09-04 06:40:42', '2022-03-14 14:17:53'),
(265899, 677, 43, 'Pour retourner un produit, il doit être dans le même état qu\'il vous a été livré: les étiquettes doivent être apposées sur les produits, ne présenter aucun signe d\'usure. Tout retour ne remplissant pas ces conditions sera refusé.', '2020-09-04 06:40:42', '2022-03-14 14:17:53'),
(265900, 677, 47, 'To return a product, it must be in the same state as it was delivered to you: the labels have to be attached to the products, have no signs of wearing. Any return that does not meet these conditions will be declined.', '2020-09-04 06:40:42', '2022-03-14 14:17:53'),
(265901, 678, 2, 'If the product you received does not look the same as the one ordered on the SHOP, we will refund the money at no additional cost to you. However, You will need to prove that the product you received does not look the same as the one ordered on the SHOP, by filling the Return form in Your Client Area and by uploading in process of filling Return form of one image, that proves that the product you received does not look the same as the one ordered on the SHOP.', '2020-09-04 06:40:42', '2022-03-14 14:17:53'),
(265902, 678, 38, 'Dacă produsul pe care l-ați primit nu arată la fel ca cel comandat în SHOP, vă vom rambursa banii fără costuri suplimentare. Cu toate acestea, va trebui să dovediți că produsul pe care l-ați primit nu arată la fel ca cel comandat în SHOP, completând formularul de retur din Cabinetul personal și încărcând în procesul de completare a formularului de retur a unei imagini, ceea ce dovedește că produsul pe care l-ați primit nu arată la fel cu cel comandat pe SHOP.', '2020-09-04 06:40:42', '2022-03-14 14:17:53'),
(265903, 678, 41, 'Если полученный вами товар не похож на тот, который был заказан в МАГАЗИНЕ, мы вернем вам деньги без дополнительных расходов с Вашей стороны. Тем не менее, вам нужно будет доказать, что полученный вами товар не выглядит так же, как тот, который был заказан в МАГАЗИНЕ, заполнив форму возврата в вашей клиентской области и загрузив в процессе заполнения форму возврата одного изображения, которое доказывает, что товар, который вы получили, не похож на тот, который был заказан в МАГАЗИНЕ.', '2020-09-04 06:40:42', '2022-03-14 14:17:53'),
(265904, 678, 43, 'Si le produit que vous avez reçu ne ressemble pas à celui commandé sur la BOUTIQUE, nous vous rembourserons l\'argent sans frais supplémentaires. Cependant, vous devrez prouver que le produit que vous avez reçu ne ressemble pas à celui commandé sur la BOUTIQUE, en remplissant le formulaire de retour dans votre espace client et en téléchargeant en cours de remplissage le formulaire de retour d\'une image, cela prouve que le produit que vous avez reçu ne ressemble pas à celui commandé sur la BOUTIQUE.', '2020-09-04 06:40:42', '2022-03-14 14:17:53'),
(265905, 678, 47, 'If the product you received does not look the same as the one ordered on the SHOP, we will refund the money at no additional cost to you. However, You will need to prove that the product you received does not look the same as the one ordered on the SHOP, by filling the Return form in Your Client Area and by uploading in process of filling Return form of one image, that proves that the product you received does not look the same as the one ordered on the SHOP.', '2020-09-04 06:40:42', '2022-03-14 14:17:53'),
(265906, 679, 2, 'If the product you ordered has manufacturing defects, you can ask for it to be refunded by filling return form in Client Area (option not available for Guest users), by phone or e-mail. The product can only be returned if it is in perfect condition (including packaging and invoice) and shows no signs of wear. The return package must contain the product in its original state, label and invoice.', '2020-09-04 06:40:42', '2022-03-14 14:17:53'),
(265907, 679, 38, 'Dacă produsul comandat are defecte de fabricație, puteți solicita rambursarea acestuia prin completarea formularului de retur în Cabinetul Personal (opțiune care nu este disponibilă pentru utilizatorii oaspeți), prin telefon sau e-mail. Produsul poate fi returnat numai dacă este în stare perfectă (inclusiv ambalajul și factura) și nu prezintă semne de uzură. Pachetul de retur trebuie să conțină produsul în starea inițială, etichetă și factură.', '2020-09-04 06:40:42', '2022-03-14 14:17:53'),
(265908, 679, 41, 'Если товар, который вы заказали, имеет производственные дефекты, вы можете запросить его возврат, заполнив форму возврата в клиентской зоне (опция недоступна для гостей), по телефону или электронной почте. Товар можно вернуть только в том случае, если он находится в отличном состоянии (включая упаковку и счет-фактуру) и не имеет признаков износа. Возвратный пакет должен содержать товар в его первоначальном состоянии, этикетку и счет-фактуру.', '2020-09-04 06:40:42', '2022-03-14 14:17:53'),
(265909, 679, 43, 'Si le produit que vous avez commandé présente des défauts de fabrication, vous pouvez demander son remboursement en remplissant le formulaire de retour dans l\'Espace Client (option non disponible pour les utilisateurs Invités), par téléphone ou par e-mail. Le produit ne peut être retourné que s\'il est en parfait état (emballage et facture compris) et ne présente aucun signe d\'usure. Le colis de retour doit contenir le produit dans son état d\'origine, étiquette et facture.', '2020-09-04 06:40:42', '2022-03-14 14:17:53'),
(265910, 679, 47, 'If the product you ordered has manufacturing defects, you can ask for it to be refunded by filling return form in Client Area (option not available for Guest users), by phone or e-mail. The product can only be returned if it is in perfect condition (including packaging and invoice) and shows no signs of wear. The return package must contain the product in its original state, label and invoice.', '2020-09-04 06:40:42', '2022-03-14 14:17:53'),
(265911, 680, 2, 'Any return request received will be reviewed and resolved in accordance with applicable legal requirements, depending on the typology of the products subject to it.', '2020-09-04 06:40:42', '2022-03-14 14:17:53'),
(265912, 680, 38, 'Orice cerere de retur primită va fi revizuită și soluționată în conformitate cu cerințele legale aplicabile, în funcție de tipologia produselor care fac obiectul acesteia.', '2020-09-04 06:40:42', '2022-03-14 14:17:53'),
(265913, 680, 41, 'Любой полученный запрос на возврат будет рассмотрен и решен в соответствии с применимыми правовыми требованиями, в зависимости от типологии товаров, на которые он распространяется.', '2020-09-04 06:40:42', '2022-03-14 14:17:53'),
(265914, 680, 43, 'Toute demande de retour reçue sera examinée et résolue conformément aux exigences légales applicables, en fonction de la typologie des produits qui y sont soumis.', '2020-09-04 06:40:42', '2022-03-14 14:17:53'),
(265915, 680, 47, 'Any return request received will be reviewed and resolved in accordance with applicable legal requirements, depending on the typology of the products subject to it.', '2020-09-04 06:40:42', '2022-03-14 14:17:53'),
(265916, 681, 2, 'We do not accept products that show signs of wear or consumption, customized products according to the customer\'s requirements, products that show physical changes, strokes, scratches, scratches, shocks, products without original packaging or damaged packaging. In order to comply with the return deadline, it is sufficient to send the notice on the exercise of the right of return before the expiry of the return period.', '2020-09-04 06:40:42', '2022-03-14 14:17:53'),
(265917, 681, 38, 'Nu acceptăm produse care prezintă semne de uzură sau consum, produse personalizate în conformitate cu cerințele clientului, produse care prezintă modificări fizice, lovituri, zgârieturi, tăieturi, produse fără ambalaje originale sau ambalaje deteriorate. Pentru a respecta termenul de returnare, este suficient să trimiteți o notificare privind exercitarea dreptului de întoarcere înainte de expirarea perioadei de returnare.', '2020-09-04 06:40:42', '2022-03-14 14:17:53'),
(265918, 681, 41, 'Мы не принимаем товары с признаками износа или потребления, товары, изготовленные по индивидуальному заказу в соответствии с требованиями заказчика, товары с физическими изменениями, ударами, царапинами, порезами, товары без оригинальной упаковки или в поврежденной упаковке. Для соблюдения срока возврата достаточно отправить уведомление об осуществлении права на возврат до истечения периода возврата.', '2020-09-04 06:40:42', '2022-03-14 14:17:53'),
(265919, 681, 43, 'Nous n\'acceptons pas les produits qui montrent des signes d\'usure ou de consommation, des produits personnalisés selon les exigences du client, des produits qui montrent des changements physiques, des coups, des rayures, des rayures, des chocs, des produits sans emballage d\'origine ou emballage endommagé. Afin de respecter le délai de retour, il suffit d\'envoyer un avis sur l\'exercice du droit de retour avant l\'expiration du délai de retour.', '2020-09-04 06:40:42', '2022-03-14 14:17:53'),
(265920, 681, 47, 'We do not accept products that show signs of wear or consumption, customized products according to the customer\'s requirements, products that show physical changes, strokes, scratches, scratches, shocks, products without original packaging or damaged packaging. In order to comply with the return deadline, it is sufficient to send the notice on the exercise of the right of return before the expiry of the return period.', '2020-09-04 06:40:42', '2022-03-14 14:17:53'),
(265921, 682, 2, 'If the return request is confirmed by us, we will refund the amount of the products that are the subject of the return request we received from you, except delivery costs no later than 14 calendar days from the date we receive back the goods. We will perform this refund using the payment method chosen by You from those listed in Return form in Your Client area or by the same payment method, used by You to pay for the order, in case this payment method is available to us and accepted by our Payment Service Provider. If You completed the order as Guest User, our Support service will inform You about available refund methods.', '2020-09-04 06:40:42', '2022-03-14 14:17:53'),
(265922, 682, 38, 'Dacă solicitarea de retur este confirmată de noi, vă vom rambursa suma produselor care fac obiectul cererii de retur pe care am primit-o de la dvs., cu excepția costurilor de livrare în cel mult 14 zile calendaristice de la data primirii înapoi a mărfii. Vom efectua această rambursare folosind metoda de plată aleasă de Dumneavoastră dintre cele enumerate în formularul de retur în Cabinetul Personalului dvs. sau prin aceeași metodă de plată, folosită de dvs. pentru a plăti comanda, în cazul în care această metodă de plată ne este disponibilă și acceptată de către Furnizorul nostru de servicii de plată. Dacă ați finalizat comanda ca utilizator invitat, serviciul nostru de asistență vă va informa despre metodele de rambursare disponibile.', '2020-09-04 06:40:42', '2022-03-14 14:17:53'),
(265923, 682, 41, 'Если запрос на возврат подтвержден нами, мы вернем сумму товаров, которые являются предметом запроса на возврат, который мы получили от вас, за исключением расходов на доставку не позднее 14 календарных дней с даты получения товара обратно. Мы осуществим возврат средств, используя выбранный вами способ оплаты из перечисленных в форме «Возврат» в разделе «Клиент», или тот же способ оплаты, который использовался вами для оплаты заказа, если этот способ оплаты доступен для нас и принят нашим поставщиком платежных услуг. Если вы выполнили заказ в качестве гостя, наша служба поддержки проинформирует вас о доступных методах возврата.', '2020-09-04 06:40:42', '2022-03-14 14:17:53'),
(265924, 682, 43, 'Si la demande de retour est confirmée par nos soins, nous vous rembourserons le montant des produits faisant l\'objet de la demande de retour que nous avons reçue de votre part, hors frais de livraison au plus tard 14 jours calendaires à compter de la date de réception de la marchandise. Nous effectuerons ce remboursement en utilisant le mode de paiement choisi par vous parmi ceux listés dans le formulaire de retour dans votre espace client ou par le même mode de paiement, utilisé par vous pour payer la commande, dans le cas où ce mode de paiement est à notre disposition et accepté par notre fournisseur de services de paiement. Si vous avez terminé la commande en tant qu\'utilisateur invité, notre service d\'assistance vous informera des méthodes de remboursement disponibles.', '2020-09-04 06:40:42', '2022-03-14 14:17:53'),
(265925, 682, 47, 'If the return request is confirmed by us, we will refund the amount of the products that are the subject of the return request we received from you, except delivery costs no later than 14 calendar days from the date we receive back the goods. We will perform this refund using the payment method chosen by You from those listed in Return form in Your Client area or by the same payment method, used by You to pay for the order, in case this payment method is available to us and accepted by our Payment Service Provider. If You completed the order as Guest User, our Support service will inform You about available refund methods.', '2020-09-04 06:40:42', '2022-03-14 14:17:53'),
(265926, 683, 2, 'The costs of returning the product (s) covered by the return request will be entirely borne by you, except the cases when it will be proven by You that the products do not look the same as the ones ordered on the SHOP or have manufacturing defects.', '2020-09-04 06:40:42', '2022-03-14 14:17:53'),
(265927, 683, 38, 'Costurile de returnare a produsului (produselor) acoperite de cererea de returnare vor fi suportate în întregime de dvs., cu excepția cazurilor în care va fi dovedit că produsele nu arată la fel ca cele comandate în SHOP sau au defecte de fabricație.', '2020-09-04 06:40:42', '2022-03-14 14:17:53'),
(265928, 683, 41, 'Расходы на возврат товара (-ов), покрываемые запросом на возврат, будут полностью покрываться вами, за исключением случаев, когда Вы докажете, что товары не похожи на те, которые заказаны в магазине, или имеют производственные дефекты.', '2020-09-04 06:40:42', '2022-03-14 14:17:53'),
(265929, 683, 43, 'Les frais de retour du ou des produits couverts par la demande de retour seront entièrement à votre charge, sauf cas où il vous sera prouvé que les produits ne sont pas identiques à ceux commandés sur la BOUTIQUE ou présentent des défauts de fabrication .', '2020-09-04 06:40:42', '2022-03-14 14:17:53'),
(265930, 683, 47, 'The costs of returning the product (s) covered by the return request will be entirely borne by you, except the cases when it will be proven by You that the products do not look the same as the ones ordered on the SHOP or have manufacturing defects.', '2020-09-04 06:40:42', '2022-03-14 14:17:53'),
(265931, 684, 2, 'ORDER CANCELATION PROCEDURE', '2020-09-04 06:40:42', '2022-03-14 14:17:53'),
(265932, 684, 38, 'PROCEDURA DE ANULARE A COMENZII', '2020-09-04 06:40:42', '2022-03-14 14:17:53'),
(265933, 684, 41, 'ПРОЦЕДУРА ОТМЕНЫ ЗАКАЗА', '2020-09-04 06:40:42', '2022-03-14 14:17:53'),
(265934, 684, 43, 'PROCÉDURE D\'ANNULATION DE COMMANDE', '2020-09-04 06:40:42', '2022-03-14 14:17:53'),
(265935, 684, 47, 'ORDER CANCELATION PROCEDURE', '2020-09-04 06:40:42', '2022-03-14 14:17:53'),
(265936, 685, 2, 'Once placed, the order cannot be changed. However, You have the right to cancel it. Remember, that in any minute after the order was placed, it might be already in process of shipping. Reason why, if You decided to cancel it, please contact our Support service by contacts displayed on our Contacts page or within this policy, as soon as possible.', '2020-09-04 06:40:42', '2022-03-14 14:17:53'),
(265937, 685, 38, 'Odată plasată, comanda nu poate fi modificată. Cu toate acestea, aveți dreptul să o anulați. Nu uitați, că în orice minut după plasarea comenzii, s-ar putea să fie deja în proces de expediere. Motiv pentru care, dacă ați decis să o anulați, vă rugăm să contactați serviciul nostru de asistență prin contactele afișate pe pagina noastră de contacte sau în cadrul acestei politici, cât mai curând posibil.', '2020-09-04 06:40:42', '2022-03-14 14:17:53'),
(265938, 685, 41, 'После размещения заказ не может быть изменен. Тем не менее, вы имеете право отменить его. Помните, что в любую минуту после размещения заказа он может уже быть в процессе доставки. По этой причине, просим Вас как можно скорее, связатесь с нашей службой поддержки по контактам, указанным на странице контактов или в данном документе.', '2020-09-04 06:40:42', '2022-03-14 14:17:53'),
(265939, 685, 43, 'Une fois passée, la commande ne peut plus être modifiée. Cependant, vous avez le droit de l\'annuler. N\'oubliez pas que, dans une minute après la commande, elle pourrait déjà être en cours d\'expédition. Raison pour laquelle, si vous décidez de l\'annuler, veuillez contacter notre service d\'assistance par les contacts affichés sur notre page Contacts ou dans cette politique, dès que possible.', '2020-09-04 06:40:42', '2022-03-14 14:17:53'),
(265940, 685, 47, 'Once placed, the order cannot be changed. However, You have the right to cancel it. Remember, that in any minute after the order was placed, it might be already in process of shipping. Reason why, if You decided to cancel it, please contact our Support service by contacts displayed on our Contacts page or within this policy, as soon as possible.', '2020-09-04 06:40:42', '2022-03-14 14:17:53'),
