(266506, 801, 2, 'You don\'t need an account to make a purchase on our SHOP, we have the option CHECKOUT AS GUEST available. However, we strongly recommend to register/ sign in, in order to have access to Your Client Area. In Your Client Area You can view Your Order history, available promocodes, Profile data and other important information.', '2020-10-20 15:10:07', '2022-03-14 14:17:54'),
(266507, 801, 38, 'Nu aveți nevoie de un cont pentru a face o achiziție din magazinul nostru, avem opțiunea ORDER AS GUEST disponibilă. Cu toate acestea, vă recomandăm să vă înregistrați / să intrați în cont, pentru a avea acces la Cabinetul Personal. În Cabinetul Personal puteți vizualiza istoricul comenzilor dvs., promocoduri disponibile, date de profil și alte informații importante.', '2020-10-20 15:10:07', '2022-03-14 14:17:54'),
(266508, 801, 41, 'Вам не нужна учетная запись для совершения покупки в нашем МАГАЗИНЕ, у нас есть опция CHECKOUT AS GUEST. Тем не менее, мы настоятельно рекомендуем зарегистрироваться / войти, чтобы иметь доступ к вашей клиентской зоне. В своей клиентской зоне вы можете просмотреть историю ваших заказов, доступные промокоды, данные профиля и другую важную информацию.', '2020-10-20 15:10:07', '2022-03-14 14:17:54'),
(266509, 801, 43, 'Vous n\'avez pas besoin d\'un compte pour effectuer un achat sur notre BOUTIQUE, nous avons l\'option CHECKOUT AS GUEST disponible. Cependant, nous vous recommandons fortement de vous inscrire / vous connecter afin d\'avoir accès à votre espace client. Dans votre espace client, vous pouvez afficher l\'historique de votre commande, les codes promotionnels disponibles, les données de profil et d\'autres informations importantes.', '2020-10-20 15:10:07', '2022-03-14 14:17:54'),
(266510, 801, 47, 'You don\'t need an account to make a purchase on our SHOP, we have the option CHECKOUT AS GUEST available. However, we strongly recommend to register/ sign in, in order to have access to Your Client Area. In Your Client Area You can view Your Order history, available promocodes, Profile data and other important information.', '2020-10-20 15:10:07', '2022-03-14 14:17:54'),
(266511, 802, 2, 'Once placed, the order cannot be changed. However, You have the right to cancel it. Remember, that in any minute after the order was placed, it might be already in process of shipping. Reason why, if You decided to cancel it, please contact our Support service by contacts displayed on our Contacts page, as soon as possible.', '2020-10-20 15:10:07', '2022-03-14 14:17:54'),
(266512, 802, 38, 'Odată plasată, comanda nu poate fi modificată. Cu toate acestea, aveți dreptul să o anulați. Nu uitați, că în orice minut după plasarea comenzii, s-ar putea să fie deja în proces de expediere. Motiv pentru care, dacă ați decis să o anulați, vă rugăm să contactați serviciul nostru de asistență prin contactele afișate pe pagina noastră de contacte, cât mai curând posibil.', '2020-10-20 15:10:07', '2022-03-14 14:17:54'),
(266513, 802, 41, 'После размещения заказ не может быть изменен. Тем не менее, вы имеете право отменить его. Помните, что в любую минуту после размещения заказа он может уже быть в процессе доставки. По этой причине, если Вы решили отменить его, как можно скорее скорее сообщите нам об этом, связавшись с нашей службой поддержки по контактам, указанным на странице контактов.', '2020-10-20 15:10:07', '2022-03-14 14:17:54'),
(266514, 802, 43, 'Une fois passée, la commande ne peut plus être modifiée. Cependant, vous avez le droit de l\'annuler. N\'oubliez pas que, dans une minute après la commande, elle pourrait déjà être en cours d\'expédition. Raison pour laquelle, si vous avez décidé de l\'annuler, veuillez contacter notre service d\'assistance par les contacts affichés sur notre page Contacts, dès que possible.', '2020-10-20 15:10:07', '2022-03-14 14:17:54'),
(266515, 802, 47, 'Once placed, the order cannot be changed. However, You have the right to cancel it. Remember, that in any minute after the order was placed, it might be already in process of shipping. Reason why, if You decided to cancel it, please contact our Support service by contacts displayed on our Contacts page, as soon as possible.', '2020-10-20 15:10:07', '2022-03-14 14:17:54'),
